e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:27:59.000Z","msg":"其實好有興趣知你咩樣 你係咪冇社交？？<br />\n<br />\n你個人係咪好悶？好冇自信？<br />\n<br />\n點解要淨係識讀書？"},{"pid":"17d874a7408a5e5f707b81a813aa0764e63f49d1","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"你們根本不明白 如果你們明白就不會這樣說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24d1d901472a45f94cabbc310a36de44c90cc98","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:30:52.000Z","msg":"反正我比所有人優越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d5fcf4c73e3d80a7788036c8c5b9a46736722d","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> tg小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> crrto<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />crrtomobile<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎隨時搵禾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa0a912c7d90d9934504d6f41f11441dcf43230","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"每個人都有自己的目標，不論是短期或長期。例如：入big4、追first hon、今個sem過3等等。<br />\n<br />\n對我來說時間分配是十分重要的，開sem時已預算了未來每一日的溫習內容，timetable密密麻麻的。<br />\n<br />\n除了major的workload外，我會定期學習英語和自學寫程式，我相信日後的作用<br />\n很大，提升英文可以學習時更暢順，一些小程式又會加倍英文學習和其他科目速度，還有很多好處，若學會了數學和統計學，可以用程式來分析金融。<br />\n<br />\n開學了，我應該怎樣分配時間學習這些東西？<br />\n我的目標是sem GPA&gt;3.5 想做finance<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7c092554eb56f8db85bac8a9f9cca041c270ed3","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:32:02.000Z","msg":"真的受不了那些要把簡單的事情重覆解釋數遍的lecturer<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該增設精英lecture和tutorial 上課時間減少一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e2e1e0d09d1a2c707686077bda182ae41c24e8","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"你班毒撚冇女可以專心讀書<br />\n<br />\njealous 😂😂"},{"pid":"6135196838b3885cc5a91ee47ebca681c114440b","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"你讀書讀到傻撚咗？"},{"pid":"08d73af46bd72733bed7e7a67fe1060541b2e17c","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ced2866c9cd396502644dd565d634a7bf27fffe","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"你不可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa3913c945509a8cc3bf48af4fdb8c608da9d11","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:33:56.000Z","msg":"你真的很醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330392709e2e23659fb229f1142d89fe25c4c6b5","tid":762693,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r